data.description: Are you ready to get out of the city, tired of the postage stamp lots? Here is a perfect opportunity to spread out on this wonderful 2.27 acre property. BRAND NEW WELL TO BE INSTALLED BY CLOSE OF ESCROW. If you have horses or are wanting animals the current owner has already built the fencing. This spacious 4 bedroom, 3 bath house has plenty of room for everyone. Both interior and exterior recently painted white. Master bedroom gives privacy in separate wing. Kitchen updated with butcher block counter tops, new stainless steel appliances, LVP flooring and a banquette seating area. Updated bathroom by the 3 bedrooms, The home floor plan flows nicely and the home has some amazing architectural features. Hosting your family and friends will be a treat once you create your back yard oasis since it is a blank slate awaiting your creativity. This home needs some finishing touches to make it your own so perfect for the handyman. Property is already zoned to have a 2nd residence for those wanting to build an Accessory Dwelling Unit.
